CAMS-2736 Ensure Consistent Application of Designated Professional Services Exclusion across General Liability and Umbrella Policies ZC 3339 and ZC 3676
Requirements:
R1) As a product user, I want the system to automatically validate and add the Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3676 in the umbrella sub-line when Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3339 is present on the General Liability (GL) sub-line.
R2) VAL-559 to be triggered when there is a duplicate entry in the list of schedule items or a mismatch in the number of schedule items between the two exclusions. Please see the attached excel sheet for scenarios.
R3) UW-418 needs to be triggered when the user tries to price with ZC3339 exclusion in Liability but without ZC3676 exclusion in Umbrella.
Acceptance Criteria 1:
As a
Product user
when I
add Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3339 is added to the General Liability (GL) policy, and the umbrella sub-line is selected
then I want
the Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3676 to be added as a suggested exclusion.
Acceptance Criteria 2:
As a
Product user
when I
see Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3676 already selected
then I want
the ability to remove the Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3676 from umbrella.
Acceptance Criteria 3:
As a
Product user
when I
remove Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3339 is added to the General Liability (GL) policy, and the umbrella sub-line is selected
then I want
the Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3676 to be removed from Umbrella.
Acceptance Criteria 4:
As a
Product user
when I
try to price the policy having both Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3339 and Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3676
then I want
the VAL-559 to be triggered when there is a duplicate entry in the list of schedule items or a mismatch in the number of schedule items between the two exclusions. Please see the attached excel sheet for scenarios.
Acceptance Criteria 5:
As a
Product user
when I
try to price the policy having Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3339 and not having Exclusion - Designated Professional Services ZC 3676
then I want
the UW-418 to be triggered blocking the quote.